com.deliveredtechnologies.rulebook.spring

Annotation Type RuleBean


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Component
 @Scope(value="prototype")
public @interface RuleBean
    Created by clong on 2/23/17. RuleBean is an annotation for Spring enabled POJO rules. This should be used to annotate POJOs that can be converted to Rules using RuleBookRunner and that are expected to be injected using Spring.
